<div class="ps-3">
  <br>
  <h1 class="custom-centered">
    Welcome this Savings Calculator</h4><br>
</div>
<br>

<body>
  <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-4">
    <div class="box">
      <h2>How does this tool calculate growth?</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Take an initial deposit (x)</li>
        <li>For each month (m) take the previous month's value (x)</li>
        <li>Multiply by the monthly interest rate (r).</li>
        <li>Add the monthly contribution (c) to it</li>
        <li>Repeat this for the number of months (t) you have selected</li>
        <li>The overall formula is: x<sub>m</sub> = x<sub>m-1</sub> * (1+r) + c</li>
        <li>It stops when the number of months (t) is reached</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="box">
      <h3>How to use this tool:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>From the top of the page, select "Add Savings Entry"</li> 
        <li>Create and save a savings journey</li>
        <li>View this entry by selecting "View Saved Entries"</li>
        <li>You can edit the entry, or delete it from this page</li>
        <li>Select "View Graph" to visualise this entry's growth over time</li>
        <li>Select "Compare Entries" to see multiple entries at the same time</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="d-flex justify-content-center mt-4">
  <%= image_tag "Example Graph 2", alt: "Graph Image", class: "img-fluid", style: "width: 50%; height: auto; border: 2px solid #000;" %>
  </div>

</body>

<% if user_signed_in? %> 

<% else %>
  <br>
  <div class="d-flex custom-centered">
    <h4>Please sign in to begin:</h4>
  </div>

  <div class="d-flex custom-centered">
    <%= button_to "Sign in", new_user_session_path, class: "logout-button" %> 
  </div>
<% end %>
